## Goal
Define the DocuSign connector’s **mechanical manifest contract** under FCP2.

## Required contents
- Manifest archetypes (closed set):
  - `operational` (envelope CRUD, send/void)
  - `streaming` (Connect webhooks/events)
- Operation list + schema IDs.
- Capability families + per-operation required caps.
- NetworkConstraints:
  - pin DocuSign API host(s) (demo vs prod are distinct)
  - pin document download hosts
  - HTTPS-only; deny redirects by default
- State model declaration:
  - webhook idempotency and envelope status tracking state (if persisted)

## Acceptance criteria
- Another engineer can implement `--manifest` from this bead alone.
